        ArtifactGCTask["WorkflowArtifactGCTask"]
    end

    %% Users/Consumers
    DSP["Data Science Pipelines"] -->|creates| WorkflowCR
    User["User / Client"] -->|submits via API| Server

    %% Controller watches CRDs
    WorkflowCR -->|watched by| Controller
    CronWorkflow -->|watched by| Controller
    WorkflowTemplate -->|read by| Controller
    ClusterWorkflowTemplate -->|read by| Controller
    WorkflowTaskSet -->|managed by| Controller
    WorkflowTaskResult -->|collected by| Controller
    ArtifactGCTask -->|managed by| Controller
    WorkflowEventBinding -->|watched by| Server

    %% Controller creates resources
    Controller -->|creates| StepPod["Workflow Step Pods"]
    Executor -->|runs in| StepPod

    %% External Dependencies
    Controller -->|watches/creates| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]
    Server -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI
    Executor -->|reports status| K8sAPI

    %% Optional Dependencies
    Executor -->|upload/download| S3["S3/Artifact Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]
    Controller -.->|archive| DB["PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP"]
    Server -.->|query archive| DB
    Server -.->|SSO auth| OIDC["OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|scrapes| Controller

